<div class="fc-landing-page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="fc-hero">
    <div class="fc-container">
      <div class="fc-eyebrow">A Curated Collection of Rare Excellence</div>
      <h1 class="fc-hero-title">For Readers Who Have <span>Read Everything Else</span></h1>
      <p class="fc-hero-subtitle">5 rare, essential, and deeply rewarding works that resist easy categorization — for the reader who demands the very best.</p>

      <div class="fc-books-display">
        {% for handle in bundle_handles %}
          {% assign current_product = all_products[handle] %}
          {% if current_product != empty %}
            <div class="fc-book-wrapper">
              <img src="{{ current_product.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ current_product.title }}" class="fc-book-cover">
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="fc-btn-container">
        <a href="#checkout-section" class="fc-btn" style="display:inline-block; max-width:420px; padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
          Claim The Final Collection →
        </a>
        <span class="fc-btn-subtext">Save over 30% instantly vs buying individually.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- THESIS -->
  <div class="fc-container">
    <div class="fc-thesis">
      <div class="fc-divider">
        <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
        <div class="fc-divider-icon">◆</div>
        <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
      </div>
      <h2>The Most Overlooked Books Are Often the Best</h2>
      <p>The bestseller list rewards what is comfortable and familiar. The truly adventurous reader knows that the most extraordinary literary experiences often come from <strong>books that don't fit neatly into a category</strong> — ancient Roman epic, Nobel Prize-winning Arabic fiction, stream-of-consciousness Southern Gothic, postmodern Italian labyrinth, and rare psychoanalytic theory.</p>
      <p>This final collection celebrates literary depth, strangeness, and ambition. These are not easy reads. They are <strong>permanent reads</strong> — books that will stay with you, challenge you, and reward every reader who commits to them.</p>
      <div class="fc-divider" style="margin-top:2rem; margin-bottom:0;">
        <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
        <div class="fc-divider-icon">◆</div>
        <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BOOK BREAKDOWNS -->
  <section class="fc-section">
    <div class="fc-container">
      <h2>Inside The Final Collection</h2>

      <!-- Book 1: The Aeneid -->
      {% assign p = all_products['the-aeneid'] %}
      {% if p != empty %}
      <div class="fc-breakdown-card">
        <img src="{{ p.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ p.title }}" class="fc-breakdown-img">
        <div>
          <span class="fc-book-tag">Roman Epic</span>
          <h3>The Aeneid</h3>
          <p>Virgil's foundational Latin epic — the story of Aeneas, Troy's fallen warrior, and his destiny to found the Roman Empire. The great companion and answer to Homer's Iliad.</p>
          <ul class="fc-checklist">
            <li>The cornerstone of the Western epic tradition alongside The Iliad and Odyssey.</li>
            <li>Virgil's meditation on duty, fate, loss, and the cost of empire.</li>
            <li>The book that shaped Dante, Milton, and all of Western literature that followed.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- Book 2: Palace Walk -->
      {% assign p = all_products['palace-walk-the-cairo-trilogy-volume-1'] %}
      {% if p != empty %}
      <div class="fc-breakdown-card">
        <img src="{{ p.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ p.title }}" class="fc-breakdown-img">
        <div>
          <span class="fc-book-tag">Nobel Prize · Arabic Literature</span>
          <h3>Palace Walk</h3>
          <p>Naguib Mahfouz's Nobel Prize-winning Cairo Trilogy begins here — an intimate portrait of an Egyptian family across three turbulent decades of colonial history. The Great Arab Novel.</p>
          <ul class="fc-checklist">
            <li>The novel that brought Arabic literature to the world stage.</li>
            <li>A richly textured, Dickensian portrait of Cairo's Al-Gamaliyya quarter.</li>
            <li>The first book of Mahfouz's greatest work — impossible to put down after the first chapter.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- Book 3: As I Lay Dying -->
      {% assign p = all_products['as-i-lay-dying-the-corrected-text'] %}
      {% if p != empty %}
      <div class="fc-breakdown-card">
        <img src="{{ p.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ p.title }}" class="fc-breakdown-img">
        <div>
          <span class="fc-book-tag">Southern Gothic</span>
          <h3>As I Lay Dying</h3>
          <p>William Faulkner's startling, innovative masterpiece: 15 different narrators tell the story of the Bundren family's harrowing journey to bury their matriarch across the Mississippi heartland.</p>
          <ul class="fc-checklist">
            <li>One of the greatest formal experiments in modern fiction.</li>
            <li>Faulkner's stream-of-consciousness at its most gripping and human.</li>
            <li>A dark comedy, a tragedy, and a profound portrait of grief — all at once.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- Book 4: The Island of the Day Before -->
      {% assign p = all_products['the-island-of-the-day-before'] %}
      {% if p != empty %}
      <div class="fc-breakdown-card">
        <img src="{{ p.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ p.title }}" class="fc-breakdown-img">
        <div>
          <span class="fc-book-tag">Postmodern · Umberto Eco</span>
          <h3>The Island of the Day Before</h3>
          <p>Umberto Eco at his most dazzling — a 17th-century nobleman shipwrecked within sight of an island he cannot reach, drifting between memory, obsession, and philosophical longing.</p>
          <ul class="fc-checklist">
            <li>A labyrinthine, baroque meditation on identity, time, and desire.</li>
            <li>Eco's virtuoso command of historical detail and postmodern narrative.</li>
            <li>For readers who loved The Name of the Rose and want to go deeper.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      <!-- Book 5: Therapeutic Action -->
      {% assign p = all_products['therapeutic-action-an-earnest-plea-for-irony'] %}
      {% if p != empty %}
      <div class="fc-breakdown-card">
        <img src="{{ p.featured_image | img_url: '400x' }}" alt="{{ p.title }}" class="fc-breakdown-img">
        <div>
          <span class="fc-book-tag">Psychoanalytic Theory</span>
          <h3>Therapeutic Action: An Earnest Plea for Irony</h3>
          <p>A rare, nuanced, and beautifully written psychoanalytic text on what actually creates change in therapy — a compelling argument for embracing ambiguity, irony, and uncertainty in clinical practice.</p>
          <ul class="fc-checklist">
            <li>Challenges mechanistic, protocol-driven approaches to therapy.</li>
            <li>A sophisticated case for the irreducibly human dimensions of therapeutic work.</li>
            <li>Essential reading for any depth-oriented clinician or psychoanalytic student.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
  <section class="fc-section" style="background:#0f0d09; border-top:1px solid #1c1408;">
    <div class="fc-container">
      <h2>What Readers Are Saying</h2>
      <div class="fc-reviews">
        <div class="fc-review-card">
          <div class="fc-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="fc-review-text">"Palace Walk is one of the greatest novels I have ever read. Mahfouz deserved his Nobel Prize ten times over. An extraordinary collection — this bundle contains some truly hidden gems."</p>
          <p class="fc-review-author">— Prof. David H., Arabic Literature, SOAS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fc-review-card">
          <div class="fc-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="fc-review-text">"As I Lay Dying broke every expectation I had for what a novel could do. The Aeneid beside it is a revelation. Five books that together feel like a complete literary education."</p>
          <p class="fc-review-author">— Catherine R., Professor of Comparative Literature</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fc-review-card">
          <div class="fc-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="fc-review-text">"Therapeutic Action is the most honest and intellectually courageous psychoanalytic text I have read in years. The Eco is pure brilliance. These are not mainstream books — they are the best books."</p>
          <p class="fc-review-author">— James W., LCSW, Private Practice</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHECKOUT -->
  <section class="fc-section" id="checkout-section">
    <div class="fc-container">
      <div class="fc-pricing-hero">
        <div class="fc-divider" style="margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
          <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
          <div class="fc-divider-icon" style="color:#d97706;">◆</div>
          <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
        </div>
        <h2>Complete Your Library</h2>
        <p>The final 5 essential reads — all in one collection.</p>

        <div class="fc-price-block">
          <span class="fc-price-current">{{ bundle_price | money }}</span>
          {% if total_compare_price > bundle_price %}
            <span class="fc-price-original">{{ total_compare_price | money }}</span>
            <br/>
            <div class="fc-savings-badge">
              You Save {{ total_compare_price | minus: bundle_price | money }} By Bundling Today
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="fc-btn-container" style="max-width:500px; margin:2rem auto 0;">
          {% form 'cart', cart %}
            {% for handle in bundle_handles %}
              {% assign current_product = all_products[handle] %}
              {% if current_product != empty %}
                {% assign variant = current_product.first_available_variant %}
                <input type="hidden" name="updates[{{ variant.id }}]" value="1" />
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
            <input type="hidden" name="checkout" value="Checkout" />
            <button type="submit" class="fc-btn" style="width:100%; max-width:480px;">
              Proceed to Secure Checkout
            </button>
          {% endform %}
        </div>

        <p style="color:#44403c; font-size:0.875rem; margin-top:1.5rem; margin-bottom:0; font-family:-apple-system,sans-serif;">
          30-Day Money-Back Guarantee. Encrypted Checkout.
        </p>

        <div class="fc-trust-icons">
          <div class="fc-trust-icon">
            <svg style="width:1.125rem;height:1.125rem;color:#d97706;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
            Encrypted Checkout
          </div>
          <div class="fc-trust-icon">
            <svg style="width:1.125rem;height:1.125rem;color:#d97706;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" /></svg>
            Instant Processing
          </div>
          <div class="fc-trust-icon">
            <svg style="width:1.125rem;height:1.125rem;color:#d97706;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
            30-Day Guarantee
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fc-divider" style="margin-top:3rem; margin-bottom:0;">
          <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
          <div class="fc-divider-icon" style="color:#78350f;">◆</div>
          <div class="fc-divider-line"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STICKY BAR -->
  <div class="fc-sticky-bar" id="fc-sticky-bar">
    <span class="fc-sticky-title">The Final Chapter Collection</span>
    <span class="fc-sticky-price">{{ bundle_price | money }}</span>
    {% form 'cart', cart, class: 'fc-sticky-form' %}
      {% for handle in bundle_handles %}
        {% assign current_product = all_products[handle] %}
        {% if current_product != empty %}
          {% assign variant = current_product.first_available_variant %}
          <input type="hidden" name="updates[{{ variant.id }}]" value="1" />
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <input type="hidden" name="checkout" value="Checkout" />
      <button type="submit" class="fc-btn" style="width:auto; padding:0.75rem 1.75rem; font-size:1rem;">
        Buy Now
      </button>
    {% endform %}
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  (function() {
    var bar = document.getElementById('fc-sticky-bar');
    var checkout = document.getElementById('checkout-section');
    document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(function(a) {
      a.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        var t = document.querySelector(a.getAttribute('href'));
        if (t) { e.preventDefault(); t.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' }); }
      });
    });
    window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
      if (bar && checkout) {
        var top = checkout.getBoundingClientRect().top;
        if (window.scrollY > 500 && top > window.innerHeight) {
          bar.classList.add('visible');
        } else { bar.classList.remove('visible'); }
      }
    });
  })();
</script>
